OL,7,FOnce again, women across the UK are
OL,8,Fstruggling to secure their hormone
OL,9,Freplacement therapy (HRT) prescriptions
OL,10,Fas a fresh wave of shortages hits the
OL,11,Fcountry.
OL,13,FRoughly two million women in the UK
OL,14,Ftake HRT to help them deal with
OL,15,Fsymptoms caused by the menopause, which
OL,16,Fcan be severe. However, supply of the
OL,17,Fmedication has been beset by
OL,18,Fchallenges, with manufacturers
OL,19,Fseemingly failing to keep up with a
OL,20,Fgrowing demand for the treatment.
